title: Developer Board 4 Version 3
description: The Developer Board 4 Version3 is a 96Boards compliant community board based on Qualcomm® Snapdragon Quad-core ARM Cortex-A53 64-bit application processors with 512kB L2 cache,1GB or 2GB LPDDR3 533MHz,8GB or 16GB eMMC 5.0,support WiFi & LAN, USB, SD/TF card external storage.The mezzaning board defines a 60Pin high-speed connector, a 40pin low-speed connector and a 16pin analog connector.
